<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15881</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹在海浪中拼命游着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他是木头做的，所以能浮在水面上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，海浪把他推来推去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰佩托的船还是离他很远。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不可能追上杰佩托的船了！”匹诺曹喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的嘴里满是咸咸的海水，他的胳膊已经酸了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40311</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他继续游着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40312</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到旁边有一座小岛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43212</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他游向小岛，打算休息一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹坐在小岛上，他寻找着杰佩托的船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，爸爸……你在哪儿？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64411</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等等，我看到你了！有一只鲸鱼在船旁边……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天啊！那只鲸鱼吞掉了你的船！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹再也看不到杰佩托了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他认为杰佩托已经掉进了水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，爸爸！我救不了你！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>对不起！呜呜呜！”匹诺曹哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，天下起了雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，我需要弄干自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸一定希望我安全地待在干燥的地方。”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向附近的村庄跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思，先生。”他对一个拉着煤车的男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能暂时待在您的家里吗？我需要一个避雨的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你能帮我拉这辆煤车，你今晚就可以住在我家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，我不想拉煤车！”匹诺曹抗拒地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他希望自己不用干活就可以得到那个男人的帮助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雨下得更大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140993</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好意思，女士。”他向一位拿着水壶的女士说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能在您家停留片刻吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你帮助我拿水壶，你今晚就可以待在我家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹不想拿水壶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他想待在一个可以避雨的地方，所以他同意了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水壶非常重，但是匹诺曹没有抱怨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一路上，他拿着水壶，直到到达女人的小屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他进屋后坐下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“水壶在这里。谢谢您收留我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用谢。”女人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“干点活儿没有什么坏处。知道吗，匹诺曹？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193558</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道我的名字？”他吃惊地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人掀开了帽子，漂亮的蓝头发露了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，蓝色小仙女！是你！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你为什么要让我干活儿？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为什么你不帮助我？”匹诺曹问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我帮助了你，匹诺曹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从陌生人那里得到帮助是好事，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是帮助陌生人是件更好的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望你记住这一点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你沿着我指的路走了吗？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我试着沿着那条路走下去。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244414</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我掉进过陷阱，在天上飞过，还游了泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263497</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我停下来休息的时候，我看到爸爸被鲸鱼吃掉了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263498</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹说到这里，忍不住开始哭泣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别哭了，匹诺曹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你的爸爸很安全，他只是被藏起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会帮助你找到他。”蓝色小仙女说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸还活着？我们现在就出发吧！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，杰佩托现在很安全。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先我们应该做的，是吃晚餐，然后睡一觉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天我们就会变得更强壮。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望我能更大，更强壮。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我变得更大，更强壮，我就能救爸爸了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，我只是一块儿木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325340</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望我是一个能长大成人的真正的男孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325341</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你是一个听话的好孩子，也许你就会变成一个真正的男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>334388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是现在，你必须睡觉，匹诺曹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>347612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天可是重要的一天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>